        <p class="text-text-secondary mb-6">Par is determined by ticket count. It sets the expected difficulty <em>before</em> the sprint begins.</p>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-emerald/20 bg-emerald/5 p-5 text-center">
            <div class="font-heading font-extrabold text-3xl text-emerald mb-1">Par 3</div>
            <div class="text-text-muted text-sm">1-2 tickets</div>
            <div class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-2">Single package, familiar area</div>
