            <div class="font-heading font-extrabold text-3xl text-red-400 mb-1">Par 5</div>
            <div class="text-text-muted text-sm">5+ tickets</div>
            <div class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-2">New infrastructure, cross-cutting</div>
